My personal vimdot files (see the vimcast on vimcast.org for details)

To get it, delete or move out of the way your  ~/.vim directory.

Then:

git clone https://github.com/svenXY/dotvim.git ~/.vim

ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
# ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

# make sure all helpfiles are tagged 
for i in ~/.vim/bundle/*/doc; do vim -c "helptags $i/" -c q; done

